  "detailed_description": "The Math Challenge is the perfect combination of animation and video game. Embark on an exciting space adventure as an astronaut, where logic and mathematics are the keys to survival. In this first chapter, we will put you to the test with magic squares. Complete the three magic squares following the specified requirements.<br><br>Enjoy a classic animation that will present you with a thrilling story set in the space race.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/5abb516f28c0109c376a769c1ff6549f.poster.avif?t=1732730654\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/5abb516f28c0109c376a769c1ff6549f.webm?t=1732730654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/5abb516f28c0109c376a769c1ff6549f.mp4?t=1732730654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Perfectly integrated with the animation, we will present you with different mathematical games that you must overcome to continue with the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/37a4e7bc4bb9bb2f350f9061f4397cf1.poster.avif?t=1732730654\" width=642 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/37a4e7bc4bb9bb2f350f9061f4397cf1.webm?t=1732730654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824360/extras/37a4e7bc4bb9bb2f350f9061f4397cf1.mp4?t=1732730654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We also provide the player with informative videos that will explain the mathematical theories on which the game is based.<br><br><s